title: Sex and Intimacy Therapy
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda talks with Fiona O'Farrel about sex therapy and the upcoming Sex and Intimacy Certification in the Couple and Family Therapy Program at Antioch University Seattle.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

April 23, 2018.
